dence**: \"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.43.10:8080: i/o timeout\".\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"transport is closing\", \"Error while dialing\", \"i/o timeout\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"RPC请求错误通过多次日志都显示了context canceled和transport is closing异常，说明与其他服务的通讯中断。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多条日志显示错误信息为 \\\"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\\\"。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"网络通讯故障，特别是在dial tcp时产生的i/o timeout，表明可能有网络或DNS配置的问题。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.43.10:8080: i/o timeout\\\"。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此分析显示通讯和网络故障可能是导致服务异常的主要原因。建议进一步调查网络配置和服务之间的通讯设置。", "metric_analysis_findings": "从2025年6月10日12:10到12:27之间，我们分析了异常指标数据。以下是发现的显著异常调用链：\n\n### 异常指标\n- `client_error_ratio`\n- `error_ratio`\n- `pod_cpu_usage`\n- `request`\n- `response`\n- `rrt`\n- `rrt_max`\n- `server_error_ratio`\n\n### 分析与假设\n\n1. **Frontend Service 性能问题**\n   - **组件**: `frontend-0`\n   - **原因**: `pod_cpu_usage`显著下降到0，伴随`error_ratio`和`server_error_ratio`在故障期间激增。\n   - **证据**: `error_ratio`从0增加到9.71，`server_error_ratio`从0增加到16.87；`pod_cpu_usage`下降至0。\n   \n2. **Product Catalog Service 性能问题**\n   - **组件**: `productcatalogservice-1`\n   - **原因**: 严重的`error_ratio`和`client_error_ratio`激增，`rrt`时间显著增加。\n   - **证据**: `error_ratio`从0增加到25.53，`client_error_ratio`从0增加到25.53；`rrt`从12363.96增加到9158274.27。\n   \n3. **Recommendation Service 性能问题**\n   - **组件**: `recommendationservice-1`\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max`急剧下降，显示出服务响应的严重不一致性。\n   - **证据**: `rrt_max`从15807下降到0。\n\n4. **Shipping Service 性能问题**\n   - **组件**: `shippingservice-2`\n   - **原因**: 并发的`client_error_ratio`和`error_ratio`异常提高。\n   - **证据**: `client_error_ratio`和`error_ratio`急剧上升至60。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"request\",\n    \"response\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage显著下降到0，伴随error_ratio和server_error_ratio在故障期间激增\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0增加到9.71，server_error_ratio从0增加到16.87；pod_cpu_usage下降至0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"严重的error_ratio和client_error_ratio激增，rrt时间显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio从0增加到25.53，client_error_ratio从0增加到25.53；rrt从12363.96增加到9158274.27\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max急剧下降，显示出服务响应的严重不一致性\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从15807下降到0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"并发的client_error_ratio和error_ratio异常提高\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio和error_ratio急剧上升至60\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
